{"issuance_frequency":"","notes_translated":{"fr":"Le présent audit visait à déterminer si Services partagés Canada (SPC) mettait en œuvre un cadre de politique de sécurité qui était conforme aux politiques du Conseil du Trésor (CT) concernant la sécurité et si les processus d’évaluation et d’autorisation de sécurité (EAS) étaient en place comme prévu.  L’audit portait sur le cadre stratégique de sécurité de SPC et le processus d’EAS, du 1er avril 2012 au 31 octobre 2013.\r\n","en":"The objective of this audit was to determine whether Shared Services Canada (SSC) was implementing a security policy framework that was consistent with Treasury Board (TB) policies regarding security and whether Security Assessment and Authorization (SA&A) processes were in place and working as intended.  The scope of the audit included SSC’s security policy framework and the SA&A process from April 1, 2012 to October 31, 2013.\r\n"},"issn":"","imso_approval":"true","isbn":"","creator":"","org_section":{"fr":"","en":""},"jurisdiction":"federal","private":false,"maintainer_email":"open-ouvert@tbs-sct.gc.ca","num_tags":0,"edition":"","frequency":"unknown","data_series_issue_identification":{"fr":"","en":""},"contributor":{"fr":"","en":""},"maintainer":null,"ready_to_publish":"true","id":"994c15f9-29b3-4ab0-bd88-ed9415ab513c","metadata_created":"2019-08-07T17:28:29.333826","subject":["government_and_politics"],"pspc_identification_number":"","metadata_modified":"2019-08-07T17:28:29.333836","author":null,"author_email":null,"geographic_region":[],"portal_release_date":"2019-08-07","digital_object_identifier":"","state":"active","version":null,"keywords":{"fr":["audit","cadre de politique de sécurité","processus d’évaluation et d’autorisation de sécurité"],"en":["Audit","security policy framework","Security Assessment and Authorization"]},"relationships_as_object":[],"creator_user_id":"4cfa9a9c-1d95-40eb-86f9-bc0c8ec45d1f","title_translated":{"fr":"Audit de la sécurité ministérielle","en":"Au